Rockfish catch by region and vessel type

rockfish.Rd

A dataset with annual catch of striped bass ("Rockfish") in Atlantic fishing regions between 2005 and first 3 quarters of 2023

Usage

rockfish

Format

Data frame with 234 observations of 14 variables

  • Estimate.Status Character, one of "FINAL" or

  • Year

  • Fishing.Year

  • Region

  • Common.Name

  • Fishing.Mode

  • Cumulative.Through

  • PSE.Total.Catch..A.B1.B2.

  • Does.Total.Catch..A.B1.B2..Meet.MRIP.Standard

  • Is.Total.Catch..A.B1.B2..Significantly.Different.From.0

  • Total.Catch..A.B1.B2.

  • Total.Catch..A.B1.B2..Lower.95..Confidence.Limit

  • Total.Catch..A.B1.B2..Upper.95..Confidence.Limit

  • X...Contribution.of.Imputed.Data.to.Total.Catch.Rate

Source

Data from NOAA NMFS https://www.st.nmfs.noaa.gov/SASStoredProcess/guest?_program=%2F%2FFoundation%2FSTP%2Fmrip_qry_index&qrycatch=Time+Series&subcatch=Goto+Query&qryeffort=Time+Series&qryparticipation=Select+a+Participation+Query
